title: Week 14 NFL Recap: Jalen Hurts wins in 1st start, Playoff Picture Analysis, Chiefs take over #1 seed in AFC, Raiders fire defensive coordinator (Football 12/14)
description:
As they do every Sunday, the Pick Six Superfriends link up late at night to recap all the action in the NFL. Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and John Breech cover everything you need to know from Week 14 including Jalen Hurts winning his first NFL start over Taysom Hill and the Saints as well as new #1 seeds in the NFC and AFC.
